Adadin cututtukan da ke tattare da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya karu cikin sauri a cikin EU/European Economic Area da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Adadin yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya ya nuna cewa, duk da bambancin yanayi tsakanin ƙasashe, cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga abin da ya faru a Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da gaggawa suna buƙatar ƙarin shiri don karɓar yawan adadin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da za a buƙaci kulawa, musamman a cikin kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an gano wasu mutane da ke fama da cutar sankarar bargo a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa an kamu da cutar coronavirus ta biyu da aka sani da SARS-CoV-2.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayanai na yanzu sun nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke kamuwa da COVID-19 suna fama da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato, cututtukan numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar sankarar bargo ba, kuma yawancin suna murmurewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya, COVID-19 yana haifar da mummunan rashin lafiya wanda ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da kusan kashi 6 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya ke ci gaba da rashin lafiya wanda ke buƙatar kulawa a cikin ɗakunan gaggawa.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya a asibiti daga COVID-19 ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika jimlar adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/EEA da Ingila (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa zuwa wasu ƙasashe kuma ana samun ci gaba a cikin yaduwar cutar COVID-19 a duk faɗin duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5 ga Maris, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton ƙididdigar farko na tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an tabbatar da farko uku daga Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami wasu cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin dukkan ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Ingila (UK), wanda ya haifar da 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, daga cikinsu 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Don gano yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da kuma yadda yake yaduwa gaba ɗaya
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana ba da rahoton ƙididdigar cutar COVID-19 ta kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushe mai tushe kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, ana sabunta su kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don nazarin halin da ake ciki na yawan masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
Don nuna halin da ake ciki na yawan masu cutar COVID-19, mun tattara adadin masu cutar COVID-19 na kwanaki 14, don haka muna mai da hankali kan yanayin yaduwar COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace ƙasa da aka bayar a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8:00 na dare idan aka kwatanta da Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Matsayin yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya a cikin kwanaki 14 ya kasance daidai da na lardin Hubei, China (Figure 1).
Gabaɗaya a cikin EU/EEA da UK, lambobin COVID-19 sun fara tashi a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu sannan kuma sun tashi sama a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Ƙarin Bayani).
Wannan ya fi yawaita ne saboda karuwar yawan masu cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK sun sami karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 (Ƙarin Bayani).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna kimanin adadin masu cutar COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK da Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8:00, sauran ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton jimlar adadin masu cutar kamar Italiya a makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa adadin sabbin cututtukan COVID-19 zai karu cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Canje-canje a cikin yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar tana yaduwa daidai a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan ya kasance duk da bambancin matakan gwaji na ƙasa, daidaitaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya, da bambancin yanayin cutar daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, da kuma bambancin ladabi don zaɓar waɗanda za a gwada don tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, gami da gwajin waɗanda ba su yi ba.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya sun ba da rahoton cewa kusan kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa a dakunan gaggawa kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da dakunan gaggawa a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun karɓi adadi mai yawa.
Bayanai kan asibitocin COVID-19 ko wuraren kulawa na gaggawa a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/EEA a halin yanzu a cikin kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
