Binciken 201011 ya nuna cewa akwai ɗakunan kulawa da gaggawa da na marasa lafiya masu sauƙi a Turai, daga gadaje 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 ga kowane mutum 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙarancin kayan aiki fiye da Italiya (sun sami gadaje marasa lafiya 12.5 ga kowane mutum 100,000 a 201011).
A cikin sabon fasalin na shida na ECDC Rapid Review of COVID-19 Challenges, an ba da misalai na yawan marasa lafiya da ke cikin kulawa, tare da kimantawa ga kowane memba na EU/EEA da UK na yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke asibiti da kusan kashi 90% na yawan gadajen ICU.
Tunda har yanzu wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da UK ne ke da mafi yawan marasa lafiya, kuma asibitoci da dakunan jinya galibi suna karɓar mutane daga takamaiman yanki, yakamata a sami bayanan marasa lafiya da gadajen jinya a cikin ƙididdigar yanki na 2 (NUTS-2).
Misali daga Italiya da kuma yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da gaggawa dole ne su kasance a shirye don ci gaba da yaduwar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma tare da karuwar yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ke neman kulawa, musamman a cikin masu ciwo mai tsanani, kamar yadda yake a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon binciken gaggawa na ECDC, yana da mahimmanci a yi amfani da saurin aiki da kuma matakan farko na duniya don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, don haka yin amfani da hanyoyin kariya maimakon zama a gida, saboda ƙaruwar yawan masu cutar da ake tsammani na iya hana masu yanke shawara da ma'aikatan asibiti damar yin nazari, fahimtar juna da kuma aiwatar da matakan da suka dace idan ba a dauki matakin da ya dace ba.
Binciken gaggawa na matsala yana nuna matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai wasu ƙananan damar da ƙasashe za su iya amfani da su don haɓaka matakan da suke ɗauka don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da tasirinsa ga tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba a yi hakan ba, cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya a wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya fuskantar ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar annobar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce cutar coronavirus ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ke haifarwa, ta riga ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, wanda hakan ya zama bala'i ga ɗan adam.
Kamar sauran ƙwayoyin cuta masu kama da su, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da mummunan mura (SARS) a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ana iya yada shi ta hanyar kwari kuma yana da alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya.
Amma COVID-19 ba ta da haɗari da kisa kamar SARS duk da cewa tana saurin yaduwa kuma tana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma tana shafar maza fiye da mata.
Saboda yawan adadin rahotanni game da wannan sabon cuta, wannan takaddar tana ƙoƙari ta samar da cikakken bincike mai amfani game da wannan batun da ake ci gaba da bincike.
Muna mai da hankali kan mahimman bayanai kamar ilimin cutar, abin da ke haifar da ita, cutar, yadda ake tantancewa, magani, yaduwa da rigakafi.
Ko da yake har yanzu akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fatan wannan gwajin zai taimaka wajen ganowa da kuma kawar da wannan cuta mai haɗari.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama tarihi ga duk Sinawa da aka umarce su da su zauna a gida a duk lokacin hutu da kuma makonni masu zuwa saboda annobar sabuwar cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana da kamanceceniya da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da mummunar cutar mura (SARS) a 2003; kuma Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma an sake kiran cutar da ke haifar da cutar COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma ta bazu zuwa duk ƙasar da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, sama da mutane 80,000 sun sami tabbacin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, wanda sama da 40,000 aka sallama kuma sama da 3,000 sun mutu.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine babban makiyi na duniya kuma yana iya zama mafi haɗari fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga labarai sama da 200 game da COVID-19 wanda ya haɗa da cutar da ke haifar da ita, cutar, asalinta, bincike da magani tun lokacin da aka buga rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya bayyana yanayin kwayar cutar da aka gano a cikin marasa lafiya daban-daban.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙari ya taƙaita binciken da aka riga aka yi akan wannan sabon abu kuma babban bincike.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu yi ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wasu cututtukan da ke haifar da CoV, kamar cutar mura ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda aka gano a cikin 2012).
Za mu sake nazarin darussan da muka koya har zuwa yanzu game da hana yaduwar cutar da gano musabbabinta da kuma wasu mahimman tambayoyin da ba a amsa ba.
Kwayoyin cutar CoVs, waɗanda aka fi ɗauka a matsayin ƙwayoyin cuta marasa mutuwa, suna da ƙarancin cutar ta 4 na mafi yawan cututtukan mura a kusan kashi 15 cikin ɗari.
Duk da haka, a cikin wannan karni, mun sami ɓarkewar CoVs biyu masu saurin kamuwa da mutane, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da barkewar cutar a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, sannan daga baya suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da yawan kamuwa da cuta da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yau shine annoba ta uku ta CoV a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin Hoto Hoto 1.1, an fara samun cutar sankarar bargo a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 lokacin da aka sanar da Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an buga takaddun da ke bayyana yanayin CoV.
Mutum na farko da ya mutu a Wuhan ya bayyana a ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa wasu biranen, larduna da ƙasashe makwabta.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an sanar da cewa wasu likitoci sun kamu da cutar, wanda ke nuna cewa mutane na iya kamuwa da cutar.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an sanya birnin Wuhan cikin keɓewa kuma an dakatar da duk hanyoyin sufuri.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken farko na likita game da cutar ya nuna cewa daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka isa kasuwar kayan abincin teku ta Wuhan inda ake zargin cewa wata dabba ce ta haifar da cutar.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, WHO ta ayyana cutar a matsayin bala'in kiwon lafiya na duniya.
A lokacin da aka buga wannan rahoton, cutar ta riga ta bazu ko'ina cikin China da wasu ƙasashe kusan 50 a duniya (Hoto (Hoto 2).2).
Saboda saurin yaduwar cutar, yana da wahala a tantance iyakar cutar da tasirin ta.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken cibiyoyi daban-daban na marasa lafiya 8,866 ciki har da 4,021 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 ya ba da cikakken hoto game da halin da annobar ke ciki a shafin yanar gizon (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
