Ƙari ga haka, yawan ƙwayar cuta tana sa ƙwayoyin jiki su yi yawa kuma hakan yana iya sa huhu da sauran gabobin jiki su lalace sosai, kuma wasu gabobin jiki su daina aiki, har ma su mutu.
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da cutar a cikin farkon kamuwa da cutar, wanda ya fi shafar tsofaffi da ke fama da wasu cututtuka da yawa da kuma mata masu ciki.
Sau da yawa, mutanen da ke da ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa ko kuma waɗanda ke da rashin lafiyar jiki suna da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar fiye da sauran mutane.
Matsakaicin lokacin SARS-CoV-2 kafin bayyanar cututtuka yana tsakanin kwanaki 1 zuwa 14, kuma mafi yawan lokuta tsakanin kwanaki 3 zuwa 7 bisa ga nazarin 425 na farko a Wuhan.
Koyaya, binciken marasa lafiya 1,099 ya nuna cewa tsawon lokacin bayyanar cututtuka shine kwanaki 3 gaba ɗaya kuma yana tsakanin 0 zuwa 24 days.
Wani bincike na kwanan nan, kamar yadda aka ambata a sama, ya nuna cewa tsawon lokacin bayyanar cututtuka shine kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2) dangane da ƙididdigar marasa lafiya 8,866.
Yana da mahimmanci ga hukumomin kiwon lafiya su tsara lokacin keɓewa daidai gwargwado dangane da ainihin lokacin da ake buƙata don bayyanar cututtuka, don haka hana mutane masu cutarwa amma marasa alamun cutar daga cutar wasu.
A al'adance, ana buƙatar keɓewar kwanaki 14 ga mutanen da ke da alaƙa da cutar ko waɗanda ke da kwayar cutar.
Idan aka kara wa'adin killacewa zuwa kwanaki 24?
Yawan zazzabi shine farkon alamun COVID-19, wanda zai iya kasancewa babu wata alama ko kuma ya kasance tare da wasu alamun kamar tari mai zafi, wahalar numfashi, ciwon gida, zazzabi, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, mura mai yawa, ciwon kirji, fitsari, zawo da amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami wahalar numfashi ko ƙarancin iskar oxygen a cikin jini mako guda bayan kamuwa da cutar.
Marasa lafiya masu tsanani sun sami ciwo mai tsanani na numfashi, ƙananan jini, cututtukan acidic da haemorrhage.
Marasa lafiya da ke da zazzabi ko alamun zazzabi mai tsanani, koda kuwa ba su da wata cuta ta huhu, ya kamata a fara gwada su don cutar a farkon lokacin.
Binciken ƙididdigar marasa lafiya a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa yawan alamun cutar ya kasance 98% na zazzabi, 76% na tari mai zafi, 55% na matsalolin oxygen da 3% na zazzabi; 8% na marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar na'urar numfashi.
An sami irin wannan binciken a cikin binciken biyu na kwanan nan akan kamuwa da cutar cikin iyali da kuma kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar marasa alamun cutar.
Kamar wannan binciken, binciken da aka yi a cikin 2012 na masu kamuwa da cutar ya nuna cewa masu cutar MERS-CoV sun sami zazzabi (98%), tari mai zafi (47%) da rashin iskar oxygen (55%) a matsayin alamun farko.
Amma kashi 80% na masu buƙatar na'urar numfashi sun fi na COVID-19 da yawan mutuwar MERS fiye da COVID-19.
Ana kuma lura da zawo (26%) da ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiya na MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiya na SARS, zazzabi (99%-100%), tari mai tsami (29%-75%), matsalolin iskar oxygen (40%-42%), zawo (20-25%) da ciwon makogwaro (13-25%) an lura da su a matsayin manyan alamun bayyanar cututtuka tare da kusan 14%-20% na marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar na'urar numfashi.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, yawan mutuwar COVID-19 ya kasance 2% lokacin da aka tabbatar da cutar a duniya ya kai 66,576.
Kamar dai da wannan kwayar cutar, yawan mutuwar SARS ya kai kashi 10% na mutane 8,096 da aka tabbatar a watan Nuwamba 2002.
A cikin MERS, bisa ga binciken kamuwa da cutar a watan Yunin 2012, yawan mutuwar ya kai kashi 37% na mutane 2,494 da aka tabbatar da cutar.
A cikin binciken da aka yi a baya, ƙimar ƙwayoyin cuta na asali (R0) don SARS-CoV-2 ya kasance mafi girma daga 6.47, ƙimar ƙwayoyin cuta na 95% (CI) ya kasance 5.71-7.23, yayin da R0 don SARS-CoV kawai ya kasance tsakanin 2 da 4.
