A cikin yanayin ciwon numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS), zafin jiki, tarin ruwa da kuma zubar da huhu suna haifar da rikicewar iska.
Rashin aiki na nau'ikan pinemosites na I da II yana rage yawan ƙwayoyin da ke rage sararin samaniya tsakanin jini kuma yana sa ƙwayoyin suyi koyi da su, don haka rage ƙarfin huhu don yin aiki kuma ƙara haɗarin rashin aiki.
Saboda haka, mummunan sakamako na radiation na kirji galibi yana haɗuwa da tsananin cutar.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, bincike na farko na cutar COVID-19 ya nuna zazzabin pinemositis, kumburi na ƙwayoyin huhu, ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta na numfashi, da ƙwayoyin cuta masu haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu na mai cutar da ta mutu, wanda ya dace da asalin kamuwa da cutar ta ARDS, kuma yayi kama da na SARS da MERS.
Gano RNA na SARS-CoV-2 RNA ta hanyar hanyar RT-PCR na dakin gwaje-gwaje an yi amfani dashi azaman babban ma'auni don gwajin COVID-19.
Koyaya, saboda yawan adadin sakamakon gwajin da ba daidai ba, wanda zai iya haifar da yaduwar cutar, an fara amfani da alamun a cikin gwaji (ba wai kawai a cikin RT-PCR ba) a China a ranar 13 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Wannan ya kasance daidai da gwajin SARS.
Saboda haka, haɗuwa da tarihin cututtuka, bayyanar cututtuka, gwaje-gwajen gwaje-gwaje da sakamakon binciken MRI yana da mahimmanci kuma yana da mahimmanci don tabbatar da ingancin bincike.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyar da Feng Zhang ke jagoranta ta bayyana wata yarjejeniya don amfani da tsarin CRISPR na SHERLOCK don gano SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke gano ɓangarorin RNA na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin kewayon 20 × 10-18 mol/L zuwa 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kwafi a kowace microliter na abin da aka saka) ta amfani da ma'aunin mai a cikin ƙasa da awa ɗaya ba tare da buƙatar kayan aiki masu mahimmanci ba.
Akwai fatan cewa wannan sabon tsarin zai iya haɓaka ingancinsa sosai idan aka gwada shi a cikin gwajin asibiti.
Saboda rashin sanin sabon CoV, likitoci na iya kasancewa a kusa da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a farkon lokacin gwaji yayin da suke gwada magungunan da aka bayar ko waɗanda ake so kafin magance sauran CoVs kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV da sauran cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta (Table (Table 2).2).
Wannan ya haɗa da magungunan da za a iya amfani da su tare da maganin rigakafi, maganin rigakafi, maganin kumburi, furotin da aka samo daga marasa lafiya, maganin gargajiya na kasar Sin, da kuma maganin cututtukan zuciya.
An yi niyyar amfani da ƙwayar da aka samo daga marasa lafiya da suka warke don magance cutar.
Kamfanonin harhada magunguna suna aiki da shi don samar da rigakafi da alluran rigakafi da ke magance cutar.
SARS-CoV-2 yana fara cutar da huhu da farko kuma yana iya cutar da, a ƙananan, sauran kwayoyin da ke aiki da ACE2 a matsayin mai cutarwa ga koda.
Duk da haka, rashin aiki da rashin aiki na numfashi sune manyan matsalolin lafiya da kuma manyan abubuwan da ke haifar da mutuwa.
Don haka, taimakon numfashi yana da mahimmanci don rage alamun cututtuka da ceton rayuka kuma ya haɗa da ƙarin iskar oxygen gaba ɗaya, ƙarin iskar oxygen, shigar da injin numfashi mai ƙarfi da kuma yin amfani da injin numfashi don daidaita yanayin cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke da alamun ciwon numfashi mai tsanani ya kamata su sami maganin ECMO, wanda shine madadin hanyar numfashi ta zuciya da huhu don magance waɗanda ke da ciwon zuciya ko ciwon numfashi.
Bugu da ƙari, kula da aikin koda, rigakafi da maganin cututtuka na gaba ɗaya da ƙananan jini, da kuma kula da aikin gabobin jiki masu mahimmanci suna da fa'ida ga marasa lafiya da SARS-CoV-2.
An san cewa haɓakar cytokine yana haifar da tsananin rigakafi a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da MERS.
Ƙarfafawar cytokine shine tsarin amsawar rigakafi na jiki wanda aka bayyana ta hanyar bayyanar cytokines daban-daban kamar TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, da MCP-1.
Wadannan cytokines suna haifar da ƙwayoyin rigakafi don sakin ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa waɗanda ba su da mahimmanci kuma suna da mahimmanci ga ARDS da kuma rashin aiki na kwayoyin halitta.
Rage rigakafi yana da amfani wajen magance haɓakar cytokine, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
Corticosteroids da tosislizumab, mai hana IL6 rigakafi mai ƙwayar cuta guda ɗaya, an yi amfani da su don magance haɓakar cytokine.
Sauran magungunan rigakafi don magance haɓakar cytokine sun haɗa da rage ƙarfin tsarin rigakafin T-cell; hana IFN-γ, IL-1, da TNF; hana JAK; maganin rigakafi; rage alamun cytokine 4; da magungunan da ke hana HDAC.
Magungunan ƙwayoyin cuta, kamar magungunan rigakafi, an yi amfani da su sosai don magance SARS don rage tsananin tasirin rigakafi.
Koyaya, shan magungunan ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa ba su da tasiri a cikin huhu da suka zama mummunan rauni a cikin marasa lafiya tare da SARS da COVID-19.
Maimakon haka, yana iya haifar da matsaloli masu tsanani, musamman cutar sankarar bargo (AVN), wanda ke da tasiri sosai ga maganin cutar.
Koyaya, ana ba da shawarar cewa ƙananan allurai na corticosteroids a cikin marasa lafiya masu cutar COVID-19 waɗanda ke da tsananin rauni a cikin ɗan gajeren lokaci kuma ana kiyaye su a hankali.
A lokacin da aka rubuta wannan rahoton, an gano maganin rigakafi a cikin mutum guda.
Amma allurar remdesivir, mai kama da nucleotide, ta tabbatar da amfani ga Ba'amurke da ke fama da COVID-19.
Remdesivir wani sabon maganin rigakafin cutar ne wanda Gilead ta samar don magance cututtukan da ke haifar da cutar Ebola da Marlburg.
Daga baya, an nuna cewa remdesivir yana da ikon hana sauran ƙwayoyin RNA, gami da MERS da SARS.
Bisa ga abin da aka ambata, Gilead ta ba da maganin ga China don gwaji biyu a cikin mutane da ke fama da cutar SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke da tsammanin sakamako.
Bugu da ƙari, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, da ribavirin an nuna su don magance marasa lafiya da ke da alamun rashin ƙarfi na numfashi.
Zazzabi, zawo, amai, ƙonewa da sauran matsaloli masu tsanani na iya faruwa yayin haɗuwa da lopinavir/ritonavir.
Ya kamata a lura da hulɗar waɗannan magungunan tare da sauran magungunan da ake amfani da su a cikin marasa lafiya.
An cire plasma daga marasa lafiya da suka warke ta hanyar aikin rigakafi
Tarin jini daga mutanen da suka warke daga cututtuka masu yaduwa don magance cututtukan da ke kama da su ko don hana mutane kamuwa da cutar ya daɗe.
Haka ne, marasa lafiya masu lafiya galibi suna da adadin ƙwayoyin cuta masu yawa a cikin jini.
Masu rigakafi sunadarai ne na antibody (Ig) waɗanda ƙwayoyin B ke samarwa don magance ƙwayoyin cuta da sauran ƙwayoyin cuta waɗanda ke gano kwayoyin cuta guda ɗaya kuma suna kashe su kai tsaye.
Dangane da abin da aka ambata, ana iya cire plasma daga jinin rukunin marasa lafiya da suka warke daga COVID-19 sannan a yi musu allurar rigakafi a cikin marasa lafiya 10 masu tsanani.
Alamun sun fara sauƙaƙa a cikin awanni 24, tare da raguwar kumburi da ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma karuwar iskar oxygen a cikin jini.
Amma gwaji da kuma bayyana su na da muhimmanci domin samar da damar amfani da su a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa kafin a samar da wasu magunguna.
Bugu da ƙari, saboda tasirin maganin, wasu daga cikin illolin da ke tattare da ƙwayar cuta dole ne a bincika su da hankali.
Alal misali, rigakafi zai iya sa jikin mutum ya yi tsayayya da cutar kuma ya sa a yi amfani da sinadarin cytokine, wanda zai iya zama guba mai haɗari.
Yawancin lokaci, ƙwayoyin rigakafi suna da ƙarancin jini kuma ana buƙatar ƙarin sinadarin plasma don kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
Ba abu mai sauƙi ba ne don samar da ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman da sauri don magance cutar ta duniya.
Saboda haka, yana da mahimmanci kuma mai mahimmanci a cire ƙwayoyin B daga marasa lafiya da suka warke sannan a bincika lambobin kwayoyin cuta na rigakafi mai ƙarfi ko kuma a gwada rigakafin rigakafi mai ƙarfi don daidaita su da sunadarai masu mahimmanci na kwayar cutar.
Ta haka ne za mu iya ƙarfafa ƙarfin jikinmu.
An yi amfani da maganin gargajiya na kasar Sin (TCM) don magance cututtuka daban-daban a kasar Sin tsawon dubban shekaru.
Amma aikinsa ya dogara ne akan haɗuwa da magunguna daban-daban a cikin yanayin da ya dace da tsarin bincike na TCM.
Yawancin magungunan da ke da amfani ba a san su ba ko kuma ba a san su sosai ba saboda yana da wuyar sarrafa su da kuma sarrafa su ko kuma yawan abubuwan da ke cikin su.
A halin yanzu, saboda rashin takamaiman maganin COVID-19, TCM ya zama ɗayan mahimman hanyoyin kula da marasa lafiya tare da alamun rashin lafiya da na matsakaici ko marasa lafiya da suka warke.
Misali, an gano cewa digo na Shu Feng Jie Du da Lian Hua Qing Wen na iya zama da amfani wajen magance COVID-19.
An lura da yawan warkewar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a larduna da yawa na kasar Sin waɗanda suka yi amfani da TCM a cikin kashi 87% na marasa lafiya na gida, kamar Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) da Hunan (50%), yayin da a lardin Hubei, wanda ya yi amfani da TCM a kusan kashi 30% na marasa lafiya na COVID-19, an sami ƙarancin dawo da lafiya (13%).
Amma wannan ƙididdiga ce mai mahimmanci saboda akwai wasu abubuwan da ke shafar kamar yawan marasa lafiya da rashin lafiya da za a yi la'akari da su a cikin gwajin.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Boli Zhang da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton wani bincike da ke kwatanta maganin da ke amfani da magungunan Turai da Amurka kawai da haɗin WM da TCM.
Sun gano cewa lokacin da ake buƙata don dawo da zafin jiki, warkar da bayyanar cututtuka da kuma kwantar da asibiti ya fi guntu a cikin ƙungiyar WM + TCM fiye da ƙungiyar WM kawai.
Abin sha'awa, ƙimar ƙarancin alamun bayyanar cututtuka (daga mai laushi zuwa mai tsanani) ya bayyana a cikin ƙungiyar WM + TCM fiye da ƙungiyar WM kawai (7.4% zuwa 46.2%) da ƙananan mutuwar a cikin ƙungiyar WM + TCM fiye da ƙungiyar WM kawai (8.8% zuwa 39%).
Koyaya, inganci da ingancin TCM har yanzu suna jiran ƙarin bincike a kan mutane da yawa da cibiyoyi.
Zai zama da kyau a nuna yadda magungunan ke aiki da kuma bayyana ainihin abubuwan da ke cikin magungunan TCM da ke da amfani ko dai a matsayin mai amfani ko a hade idan ya yiwu.
Masu fama da cutar COVID-19 da ake zargi ko tabbatar da su sau da yawa suna da tsananin tsoron kamuwa da cutar da ke haifar da mutuwa, yayin da waɗanda aka keɓe suna da rashin jin daɗi, kaɗaici da fushi.
Hakanan, alamun kamuwa da cuta kamar zazzabi, rashin numfashi, tari da kuma tasirin magunguna kamar rashin bacci na corticosteroids na iya haifar da damuwa da rikicewar hankali.
A farkon barkewar cutar SARS, an gano cututtukan kwakwalwa daban-daban da suka haɗa da damuwa, damuwa, tsoro, rikicewa, rikicewa, damuwa, da ƙoƙarin kashe kansa.
Binciken tuntuɓar mutum da keɓaɓɓun keɓewa a matsayin ɓangare na matakan COVID-19 na hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa na iya haifar da ƙarin damuwa da laifi game da tasirin kamuwa da cuta, keɓewa da nuna bambanci daga dangi da abokai.
Saboda haka, dole ne a ba da sabis na lafiyar hankali ga masu cutar COVID-19, waɗanda ake zargi da kamuwa da cutar da kuma waɗanda ke da alaƙa da su da kuma sauran mutanen da ke buƙatar taimako.
Kulawa da lafiyar kwakwalwa ya kamata ya kasance tare da kafa ƙungiyoyin kula da lafiyar kwakwalwa na ma'aikatun daban-daban, ingantaccen tsarin musayar bayanai na yau da kullun da ingantaccen bayani game da cutar SARS-CoV-2 da tsarin kulawa da lafiya da kuma amfani da kayan aiki da aikace-aikacen fasaha don nisantar kusanci.
Alluran rigakafi masu inganci suna da mahimmanci don hana kamuwa da cuta tsakanin dabbobi masu cutar da mutane masu cutar da wasu dabbobi ko mutane waɗanda ƙila suna da cutar kuma galibi suna aiki tare da maganin rigakafi don magance cututtukan da sabbin ƙwayoyin cuta ke haifarwa.
An riga an yi ƙoƙari don samar da alluran rigakafi na S-protein don samar da rigakafi na dogon lokaci ko haɓaka ƙarfin jiki ga SARS-CoV.
An gwada alluran rigakafi da ke amfani da ƙwayoyin cuta da aka raunana akan dabbobi don SARS.
Amma fa'idar alluran rigakafi a cikin dabbobi ko tsofaffi masu lafiya da kuma rigakafin kamuwa da ƙwayoyin cuta na dabbobi ba za a iya gano su ba har sai an gudanar da bincike na asibiti.
Wannan na iya zama saboda an daina cutar SARS shekaru 17 da suka gabata kuma babu wani sabon kamuwa da cutar.
A gefe guda, ƙananan cututtukan MERS suna ci gaba da bayyana a Gabas ta Tsakiya kuma cutar tana yaduwa zuwa wasu yankuna saboda ƙwayoyin cuta da ke ci gaba da cutar da mutane a yankunan da cutar ta fi yaduwa.
An tsara matakan rigakafin MERS ta hanyar amfani da ƙwayoyin cuta masu ƙarancin ƙarfi, DNA parasimides, kwayoyin cuta, ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta, ƙwayoyin cuta masu kama da ƙwayoyin cuta da ƙwayoyin cuta masu ɓoyewa kuma an gwada wasu daga cikin waɗannan matakan akan dabbobi.
Samun allurar rigakafin SARS-CoV-2 mai inganci da aminci ga mutanen da ke da ƙarancin rigakafi yana da mahimmanci da gaggawa don magance cutar.
Amma yana da wahala a magance wannan matsalar saboda tsayi mai yawa (kimanin watanni 18) da ake buƙata don samar da allurar rigakafi ta hanyar maye gurbin CoVs.
A matsayin sabon kamuwa da cuta, COVID-19 ya fara nuna yiwuwar warkewa a cikin dubunnan masu cutar.
Sau da yawa, marasa lafiya suna samun sauƙi ba tare da wata matsala ba.
Koyaya, kamar SARS da MERS, COVID-19 yana da yawan kamuwa da cuta da mutuwa a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
Don haka, samar da hanyoyin kula da cutar yana da mahimmanci don tabbatar da asibitoci da cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya suna iya amfani da ayyukansu yadda yakamata ko kuma a wuraren da ba su da isasshen kayan aiki.
