Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yaba wa matakin da hukumomin kasar Sin suka dauka na dakile yaduwar cutar.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ce akwai bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da yin asirin ta kuma hana matakan rigakafi da sarrafawa, da kuma barkewar cutar ta yanzu inda gwamnati "ta ba da sanarwar kai tsaye don hana fargaba kafin hutun Sabuwar Shekara".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, bayan babban jami'in ya yanke shawarar aiwatar da dokar hana fita daga Wuhan, Gauden Galea, wakilin Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, ya ce duk da cewa "ba shawarar WHO ba ce", amma "alamu ne masu karfi na kokarin dakile cutar a inda ta riga ta bayyana" kuma ya kira ta "babbar tarihi a cikin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan an tabbatar da wasu mutane a wajen China da kuma karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a wasu ƙasashe, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a ta duniya (ICHEP), wanda shine karo na shida a cikin jerin gaggawa na gaggawa na duniya saboda annobar a shekarar 2009.
Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, Tedros Adhanom, ya ce PHEIC yana da haɗarin yaduwa a duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu talauci da matsakaitan kuɗi waɗanda ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Game da aiwatar da dokar hana zirga-zirga, Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili da zai sa a hana zirga-zirgar mutane da kasuwanci" kuma "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar dakatar da zirga-zirga da zirga-zirga ba".
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta nemi ƙasashe su ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 don tallafawa shirye-shiryen yaduwar cutar a ƙasashe masu tasowa, tana mai cewa yana da gaggawa don tallafawa ƙasashe waɗanda "suna da ƙwarewar gano ƙwayoyin cuta, koda kuwa suna da ƙwarewa".
