A wannan ranar, Tedros ya sanar da cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da ba da "dukan ƙarfin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya don neman mafita".
An kafa wani rukunin kula da rikicin na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya don daidaita ayyukan Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ce zai ba da "mafificin hankali ga kula da kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya ba da gogewarsu don magance tasirin cutar ga zamantakewa, tattalin arziki, da ci gaba gaba ɗaya".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an kafa wani rukunin hadin gwiwa na WHO tare da kasar Sin don zaɓar ƙwararrun ƙwararrun ƙasashen duniya da WHO da za su tura China don taimakawa wajen kula da kula da cutar da kuma kula da cutar" ta hanyar gudanar da horo tare da manyan hukumomi da hukumomi na cikin gida da kuma ziyarar wurare don kimanta "matsayin tasirin ayyukan rigakafin cutar a larduna da yankuna ciki har da yankuna na karkara da birane".A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta ba da sanarwar cewa "duniya ta yi aiki tuƙuru don shirya don cutar coronavirus", ta ba da shawarar cewa duk da cewa cutar ta fara a farkon lokacin, ana iya kiran ƙasashe "shirye-shiryen".
Don magance yaduwar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da wata ƙungiya ta haɗin gwiwa don nazarin halin da ake ciki.A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ba da sanarwar cewa za a haɓaka ƙimar cutar coronavirus a duniya daga matakin "babba" zuwa "mafi girma", matakin gargadi da kimantawa mafi girma.
Mike Ryan, babban daraktan shirin agaji na WHO, ya yi gargadi: "Wannan ita ce ainihin ma'auni ga kowace ƙasa a duniya: Ku farka.
Cutar tana gabatowa kuma dole ne ku kasance cikin shiri", ya jaddada cewa tsauraran matakai na iya taimakawa wajen hana "hadarin da ke tattare da ita".
Ryan ya ci gaba da cewa bayanan da ake da su ba su sa hukumomin kiwon lafiya su ayyana cutar a matsayin annoba ta duniya ba, yana mai cewa yin hakan zai nuna cewa "a zahiri mun yi imanin cewa kowa a duniya zai kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga Maris, WHO ta ayyana coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO "ta damu matuka game da saurin yaduwar cutar da kuma rashin daukar matakan da suka dace". WHO ta fuskanci mummunan suka saboda rashin daukar matakan da suka dace don hana cutar, kamar sanarwar da ta yi game da matsalar lafiyar jama'a da kuma sanya kwayar cutar a cikin jerin cututtukan.
Wasu daga cikin ƙalubalen da aka fuskanta sun haɗa da neman shugaban WHO Tedros Adhanom ya yi murabus har zuwa ranar 6 ga Afrilu, wanda ya sami sa hannun mutane 733,000.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, masana kan hakkin dan adam na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun jaddada girmama haƙƙin kowane mutum a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta bayyana cewa kowane mutum na da hakkin samun kulawar lafiya kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin hakan.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin kudi ko inshorar lafiya bai kamata ya zama dalilin nuna wariya ga wata kungiya ba.
Masana sun jaddada cewa kowa yana da hakkin samun lafiya, gami da nakasassu, membobin kungiyoyin da ba su da wata dama, tsofaffi, masu gudun hijira, marasa gida, masu fama da talauci, fursunoni, har ma da 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyin da ke bukatar taimakon gwamnati.
Ƙungiyoyin ƙasa da ƙasa da gwamnatoci suna magance matsalolin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar da cutar COVID-19 ta haifar.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwa ta tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kirkiro wani dandamali don samar da cikakken bayani da kuma ingantaccen bayani game da manufofi da ke magance wannan matsalar a kasashe a duniya, da kuma ra'ayoyi da shawarwari daban-daban.
Daga manufofi don ƙarfafa cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arziki na duniya don magance tasirin dokar hana fita da rage yawan motsi, matakan da aka tsara ta hanyar fasaha sun haɗa da Tsarin Gano Masu Cutar, kuma suna nufin taimaka wa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da kuma haɗa kan dabarun duniya don magance coronavirus.
