Gwamnatin Donald Trump a Amurka ta kira coronavirus "Covid-19 na kasar Sin" ko "Covid-19 na Wuhan" a matsayin wani ɓoye-ɓoye da China ta yi don tabbatar da cutar ta zama annoba ta duniya. Amma wasu sun soki wannan a matsayin nuna bambanci da kuma ɓatar da hankali daga gazawar gwamnatin ta wajen dakile cutar.
